##############################
## MANUAL
1. get your broadcast IP address
2. Ping your broadcast IP address ping 192.168.1.255 (may require -b on Linux)
3. Now type arp -a
	You will get the list of all IP addresses on your segment.

##############################
## nmap
	$ nmap -sP 192.168.1.*
or more commonly
	$ nmap -sn 192.168.1.0/24

